<p>The update can be obtained through the following link or by using Windows Update / WSUS.</p>

<p><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4013429/windows-10-update-kb4013429" target="_blank">https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4013429/windows-10-update-kb4013429</a></p>

<p>There is also a Servicing Stack Update (SSU) for March, so if you are installing manually you must also first install KB4013418</p>

<p><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4013418/servicing-stack-update-for-windows-10-version-1607-and-windows-server-2016-march-14-2017">https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4013418/servicing-stack-update-for-windows-10-version-1607-and-windows-server-2016-march-14-2017</a></p>

